T1  - Failure to exercise call options: An anomaly and a trading game
AU  - Pool, Veronika Krepely
AU  - Stoll, Hans R.
AU  - Whaley, Robert E.
JO  - Journal of Financial Markets
VL  - 11
IS  - 1
SP  - 1
EP  - 35
